<p><b>Is ISO 9001 lead auditor certification worth it?</b> Yes, ISO Lead Auditor certification is worth pursuing. It is an internationally recognized certification that adds value to your career and will be a significant step to become a Lead Auditor professional. Also, you should have at least two years of work experience in Information Security Management to get certified.</p>
